<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeef8 0%, #fff5f9 100%);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e91e63;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .last-updated {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #d81b60;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #fce4ec;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #c2185b;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #fce4ec;
            border-left: 4px solid #e91e63;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .service-box {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #9c27b0;
        }

        .service-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7b1fa2;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 2px solid #fce4ec;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        a {
            color: #e91e63;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .table-of-contents {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .table-of-contents ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        .table-of-contents a {
            color: #d81b60;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p><strong>Flirrt.AI</strong> ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our dating conversation assistance application.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="table-of-contents">
            <h3>Table of Contents</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#section-1">1. Information We Collect</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-2">2. How We Use Your Information</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-3">3. Third-Party AI Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-4">4. Data Retention and Deletion</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-5">5. Your Privacy Rights</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-6">6. Security Measures</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-7">7. Age Verification</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-8">8. Changes to This Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section-9">9. Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 id="section-1">1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>1.1 Personal Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, Apple ID (for Sign in with Apple)</li>
            <li><strong>Age Verification:</strong> Birthdate (to verify you are 18 years or older)</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, unique device identifiers</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.2 Screenshot Data</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Dating App Screenshots:</strong> Profile screenshots and chat conversations from dating apps</li>
            <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> To analyze profiles and conversations and generate personalized flirt suggestions</li>
            <li><strong>Retention:</strong> Screenshots are stored for 30 days or until you delete them</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.3 Voice Data</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Voice Samples:</strong> Audio recordings of your voice (10-30 seconds)</li>
            <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> To create a voice clone for generating voice message suggestions</li>
            <li><strong>Retention:</strong> Voice clones are stored until you delete them or close your account</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.4 Usage Data</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>App Activity:</strong> Features used, suggestions selected, feedback provided</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> App performance, crash reports, usage patterns</li>
            <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> To improve app functionality and personalize your experience</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="section-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

        <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>AI Analysis:</strong> Analyzing screenshots to understand dating profiles and conversations</li>
            <li><strong>Suggestion Generation:</strong> Creating personalized flirt suggestions using advanced AI</li>
            <li><strong>Voice Synthesis:</strong> Generating voice messages in your voice</li>
            <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> Tailoring suggestions based on your preferences and feedback</li>
            <li><strong>App Improvement:</strong> Analyzing usage patterns to enhance features and user experience</li>
            <li><strong>Safety & Moderation:</strong> Screening suggestions for inappropriate content</li>
            <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Responding to your inquiries and providing assistance</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="section-3">3. Third-Party AI Services</h2>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Flirrt.AI uses multiple third-party AI services to provide our features. Your data may be processed by these services as described below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-box">
            <div class="service-name">OpenAI GPT-5 Pro</div>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> AI coaching persona, explanation of suggestions, conversation strategy advice</p>
            <p><strong>Data Sent:</strong> Screenshot analysis results, user preferences, conversation history (text only)</p>
            <p><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" target="_blank">https://openai.com/privacy</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-box">
            <div class="service-name">Google Gemini 2.5 Pro</div>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Profile analysis, interest extraction, visual content understanding</p>
            <p><strong>Data Sent:</strong> Screenshot images, extracted text from dating profiles</p>
            <p><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-box">
            <div class="service-name">xAI Grok-4</div>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Screenshot analysis, suggestion generation, conversation context understanding</p>
            <p><strong>Data Sent:</strong> Screenshot images, conversation context, tone preferences</p>
            <p><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://x.ai/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">https://x.ai/legal/privacy-policy</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-box">
            <div class="service-name">Perplexity Sonar Pro</div>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Real-time dating advice, topic research, current trends</p>
            <p><strong>Data Sent:</strong> User questions, conversation topics, context queries</p>
            <p><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://www.perplexity.ai/privacy" target="_blank">https://www.perplexity.ai/privacy</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-box">
            <div class="service-name">ElevenLabs Voice Synthesis</div>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Voice cloning, text-to-speech synthesis, audio message generation</p>
            <p><strong>Data Sent:</strong> Voice samples (for cloning), text for synthesis</p>
            <p><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://elevenlabs.io/privacy" target="_blank">https://elevenlabs.io/privacy</a></p>
        </div>

        <h3>3.1 Content Moderation</h3>
        <p>We use <strong>OpenAI Moderation API</strong> and <strong>GPT-5 Vision</strong> to screen all suggestions for inappropriate content, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Explicit or sexual content</li>
            <li>Harassment or pressuring language</li>
            <li>Hate speech or violence</li>
            <li>Self-harm references</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="section-4">4. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>

        <h3>4.1 Retention Periods</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Screenshots:</strong> 30 days or until you delete them</li>
            <li><strong>Suggestions:</strong> 90 days or until you delete them</li>
            <li><strong>Voice Clones:</strong> Until you delete them or close your account</li>
            <li><strong>User Profile:</strong> Until you delete your account</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> 90 days (anonymized after 30 days)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4.2 Account Deletion</h3>
        <p>You can delete your account at any time through the app settings. When you delete your account:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Your account will be immediately disabled</li>
            <li>All personal data will be deleted from our servers within 7 days</li>
            <li>Voice clones will be removed from ElevenLabs</li>
            <li>We will request data deletion from all third-party AI services</li>
            <li>You will receive email confirmation once deletion is complete</li>
        </ol>

        <h2 id="section-5">5. Your Privacy Rights</h2>

        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:</p>

        <h3>5.1 GDPR Rights (EU/UK)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate personal data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Delete your personal data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Restriction:</strong> Limit how we process your data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Object:</strong> Object to processing of your personal data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.2 CCPA Rights (California)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Right to Know:</strong> What personal information we collect and how we use it</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Delete:</strong> Request deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Opt-Out:</strong> Opt-out of the sale of personal information (we do not sell your data)</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Non-Discrimination:</strong> We will not discriminate against you for exercising your rights</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.3 How to Exercise Your Rights</h3>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:<%= contactEmail %>"><%= contactEmail %></a></p>

        <h2 id="section-6">6. Security Measures</h2>

        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Encryption in Transit:</strong> TLS 1.3 for all data transmission</li>
            <li><strong>Encryption at Rest:</strong> AES-256 encryption for stored data</li>
            <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Role-based access with audit logging</li>
            <li><strong>Regular Security Audits:</strong> Periodic penetration testing and vulnerability assessments</li>
            <li><strong>Secure Infrastructure:</strong> Hosted on enterprise-grade cloud infrastructure</li>
            <li><strong>Data Minimization:</strong> We only collect data necessary for app functionality</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="section-7">7. Age Verification</h2>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p><strong>18+ Only:</strong> Flirrt.AI is intended for users aged 18 and older. We collect and verify your birthdate during account creation to ensure compliance with age restrictions.</p>
        </div>

        <p>If we discover that a user under 18 has created an account, we will immediately:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Disable the account</li>
            <li>Delete all associated data</li>
            <li>Prevent future access</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="section-8">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>

        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Posting the new Privacy Policy in the app</li>
            <li>Sending you an email notification (if you have provided your email)</li>
            <li>Displaying a prominent notice in the app</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Your continued use of Flirrt.AI after changes to this Privacy Policy constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

        <h2 id="section-9">9. Contact Us</h2>

        <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= contactEmail %>"><%= contactEmail %></a></li>
            <li><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@flirrt.ai">support@flirrt.ai</a></li>
            <li><strong>Legal:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@flirrt.ai">legal@flirrt.ai</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Flirrt.AI. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="/api/v1/legal/terms">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="/api/v1/legal/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
